/www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/author-ODOFEl8xHVsWXQUPgj9Ktg">Liễu Vĩnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Ng%C5%A9-Ph%C3%BAc/Th%E1%BB%8D-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-b%E1%BB%93i-t%E1%BB%A5ng/poem-hUmzO1SDGW_Qfb2PyIcOjw">Thọ Nguyễn bồi tụng - 壽阮陪訟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Ng%C5%A9-Ph%C3%BAc/author-nDDIeBcr0ae9JEbukHfORA">Hoàng Ngũ Phúc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-4/poem-H3Y-d-yFQNUZW6tmsEdybw">Thường đệ 4 - 裳棣 4</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C5%A9-S%C6%A1n-v%C5%A9-b%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1c-n%C3%AA/poem-Jh0ybTlYkxJlmL_djGuRGg">Vũ (Sơn vũ bất tác nê) - 雨（山雨不作泥）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
